==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tac-au-tac
<hw>Tac`-au-tac"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>riposter du tac au tac</ets> to parry (where <ets>tac</ets>
imitates the sound made by the steel).]</ety> <fld>(Fencing)</fld>
<def>The parry which is connected with a riposte; also, a series of
quick attacks and parries in which neither fencer gains a
point.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tace</ent>⟦br⟧
